dc_title_s: River Miles: Mississippi River and Tributaries
dc_creator_sm: US Army Corps of Engineers, St. Paul District Office
dc_description_s: River miles (point data) from the Mississippi Headwaters to Lock and Dam 10, including a section of the Minnesota, St. Croix, and Black Rivers. Data has been adjusted to match the Upper Mississippi River Navigation Charts sailing line and the Channel Maintenance Base Maps (CMBM).
